# PromptForge AI 🚀

PromptForge AI is a zero-cost multi-agent AI system built using Poe's Multi-Bot orchestration framework. It converts simple application ideas into structured project specifications and detailed prompts optimized for AI-powered development platforms like Bolt.new.

The system uses two specialized AI agents:

- 🧠 **VibePrompt_Bot (Lead Agent)**  
  Acts as the project coordinator. It analyzes user requirements, communicates with the worker agent, and generates a complete development prompt.

- ⚙️ **SpecArchitect_Bot (Worker Agent)**  
  Acts as a software architect. It extracts the application's purpose, target users, features, UI requirements, and user interactions.

## Workflow

User Idea  
⬇️  
VibePrompt_Bot (Orchestrator)  
⬇️  
SpecArchitect_Bot (Specification Generator)  
⬇️  
Final Development Blueprint + Bolt.new Prompt

